{"title":"Marin’s New Larkspur E Gets Lights, Fenders, and a Bosch Motor","link":"https://bikerumor.com/marins-new-larkspur-e-bike-commuter/","date":1727967426000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-hero-jpeg.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Marin Bikes)\" /></p>\n<p>A few years back I <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/marin-larkspur-2-atb-mountain-bike-city-bike/\" target=\"_blank\">reviewed</a> a pretty unique bike from Marin Bicycles, the Larkspur. Well, now they’ve added a <a href=\"https://www.marinbikes.com/bikes/2025-larkspur-e\" target=\"_blank\">new model</a> with the Larkspur E. The new city/adventure bike is all dressed up with front and rear lights, fenders, and a Bosch Active Line Plus motor.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E first pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-first-pic-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Marin Bikes)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Larkspur E still has the spirit of the original Larkspur “adventure/mixte”, but is now ready for some serious commuting. Don’t get me wrong though, if you wanted to take the Larkspur E out on the fire roads around town, it’s up for it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E on the go\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-on-the-go-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Larkspur E is a fully capable bike on any terrain. Be it exploring the neighborhood, grabbing groceries, commuting, or venturing on gravel trails, it can handle it all.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>It Comes with Good Stuff</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E Bosch drive motor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-Bosch-drive-motor-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Larkspur E’s Bosch Active Line Plus drive unit gives a claimed range of 25-93 miles. This range depends on rider weight, the level of assistance used, and the terrain that is being ridden. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E battery\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E battery indicator\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-battery-indicator-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The battery can be fully recharged in only 4 hours. It carries a top-assisted speed of 20MPH. The different assist modes are picked on the cleanly integrated display which sits next to the left grip. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E intgrated controls\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-intgrated-controls-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The “E” part of the Larkspur E uses the Bosch Smart System, has 50Nm of torque, and a 545Wh battery. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E CUES drivetrain\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-CUES-drivetrain-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Larkspur E also sports a Shimano CUES drivetrain, which is designed to run specifically with center drive motors. Stopping power is delivered with Shimano hydraulic brakes and big 180mm rotors.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E dropper post\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-dropper-post-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It’s also equipped with a dropper post in case there is some gnar on the way home from grabbing groceries. Or more realistically, it provides a way to comfortably stop at intersections and make getting on/off easier with a lower saddle. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Larkspur E Geometry</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lark-E-geos-Large-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"1219\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lark-E-geos-Large-jpeg.webp\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lark-E-geos-Large-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lark-E-geos-Large-297x283.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lark-E-geos-Large-120x114.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Lark-E-geos-Large-768x731.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E rear light\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-rear-light-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E front light\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-front-light-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Larkspur E Highlights and Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: $2,999</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>CrMo step-thru “mixte” frame &amp; CrMo fork</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bosch Active Line Plus smart system drive unit w/ 50Nm torque</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Class 1 (North America/NZ); 20MPH top assisted speed, 25 km/h in other global markets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bosch Power Pack 545 downtube battery, 545Wh, removable with key</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano CUES 1x 10-speed drivetrain</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Shimano hydraulic disc brakes</li>\n\n\n\n<li>27.5″ wheels w/ 2.35″ wide multi-surface tires</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Full-wrap extrusion aluminum fenders &amp; integrated Lezyne lighting</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Dropper seat post</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-jpeg.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-jpeg.webp\" alt=\"Marin Bikes' new Larkspur E sipping joe\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-jpeg.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Marin-Bikes-new-Larkspur-E-sipping-joe-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.marinbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">MarinBikes.com</a></em></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/marins-new-larkspur-e-bike-commuter/\">Marin’s New Larkspur E Gets Lights, Fenders, and a Bosch Motor</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"77db50c90d973fd2bd8faa7cf33eabeae5dc818c9a5776a454e8a745ef4418d0","category":"Cycling"}